PLACEHOLDER — Previously Published Data Source
This file contains the functional phylogram for birds constructed via UPGMA clustering of morphological trait distances (Skeels & Yaxley 2023).
It is used to calculate Functional Distinctiveness (FuD) scores via evol.distinct().
Download the original tree from:
[LINK TO BE FILLED IN]
Place the downloaded file in this directory as UPGMA_functional_tree_birds.tree before running FuDGE_clean.Rmd.
